name: Jack_&_Jill_Deluxe_Toy_Box_w_Book_Rack,_Blue__Grey
description:
Roomy enough to hold toys of all shapes and sizes, the Jack & Jill Deluxe Toy Box with Book Rack from Delta Children is outfitted with a separate space for books or magazines. Featuring clean lines and a durable wood construction, it's a stylish storage option that's designed with rounded corners, smooth edges and a child-safe lid for your little one’s safety.
